description: A sunny morning in Prague. A good time to start the hunt. I took my cam and decided to wait for a tram. Line 7 was crowded – as usually. Just one stop later I left the tram following a guy which I approached inside. We had a good interview but he was too shy to go ahead. Then I realized that another boy stood next to me who was able to hear parts of my last interview. He looked good. Better then the first guy. He almost seemed to wait for me so I didn´t hesitate and started a conversation. He was clever and open-minded. So we went together to a park. He showed me his cock for a few crowns. For a few thousands he followed me into the bushes.
title: Czech Hunter 06
